Package: rcds
Title: Richard Cartographic Design System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Roland", "Richard", email = "roland.a.richard@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An opinionated cartographic design system for R. Codifies a
    consistent visual identity (dark-canvas thematic maps with a heavy
    display title face, a clean body face, a standardized signature caption,
    and patchwork main + locator + credits composition) into reusable themes,
    palette families, layout helpers, export presets, and a map-quality
    scoring rubric. Built on ggplot2, sf, ggspatial, ggtext, showtext,
    colorspace, and patchwork.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
